snippet.title: Amber Heard beams while horseback riding in LA
snippet.description: Amber Heard was spotted beaming while horseback riding in Los Angeles, as she prepares to learn if her ex-husband Johnny Depp won a libel suit against a newspaper that claimed he was a 'wife-beater' during their chaotic marriage.. .Heard had traveled to England in July to give evidence against her 52-year-old ex-husband during a high-profile, three-week hearing at London's High Court.The extraordinary case laid bare their tempestuous private lives as the court was told of allegations of serious domestic abuse, drug taking and affairs. The judgement in the 'Depp v News Group Newspapers Ltd' case will be published online at 10am on Monday and there will be no hearing at court.    .. . .The estranged couple managed to agree to a $7 million divorce settlement in August of that year, however their feud reignited when Heard's op-ed was published in December 2018.It didn’t mention Depp by name but he nonetheless sued her the following March, saying it led to speculation that he was the abuser ...
